🔥 StringUtil kya hai?
👉 StringUtil ek helper / utility class hoti hai
👉 Jo String (text) pe kaam karne ke ready-made methods deti hai

🧠 Simple Language:-
👉 "String ke saare common kaam ek jagah pe ready mil jaate hain"
/////////*
1️⃣ str.trim():-
String ke starting aur ending ke extra spaces hata deta hai
String str = "   hello   ";
System.out.println(str.trim());  // "hello"
2️⃣ .isEmpty():-
Check karta hai ki string empty hai ya nahi
String str = "";
System.out.println(str.isEmpty());  // true
*////////
--------------------------------------------------------------------
💡 Kyu use hota hai?
Normal Java me tu likhega:-
if(str != null && !str.trim().isEmpty())

👉 Lekin StringUtil me ye simple ho jata hai:-
StringUtil.isNotEmpty(str)
✅ Code clean
✅ Time save
✅ Reusable
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔥 1️⃣ Basic Check Methods:-
isEmpty(String str)
isNotEmpty(String str)
isBlank(String str)
isNotBlank(String str)
💡 Use
empty / null check

🔥 2️⃣ Safe Methods (Null-safe):-
safeTrim(String str)
safeEquals(Object o1, Object o2)
safeToString(Object obj)

🔥 3️⃣ Conversion Methods:-
stringToList(String str)
stringToList(String str, String delimiter)
listToString(List list)
listToString(List list, String delimiter)
csvToList(String str)
listToCsv(List list)

🔥 4️⃣ Join & Split:-
join(Collection col, String delimiter)
split(String str, String delimiter)

🔥 5️⃣ Default Value:-
coalesce(Object... values)
defaultIfNull(String str, String defaultVal)

🔥 6️⃣ Case Handling:-
capitalize(String str)
uncapitalize(String str)
toUpperCase(String str)
toLowerCase(String str)

🔥 7️⃣ Trim / Clean:-
trim(String str)
trimToNull(String str)
trimToEmpty(String str)

🔥 8️⃣ Replace / Remove:-
replace(String str, String search, String replace)
remove(String str, String remove)
removeWhitespace(String str)

🔥 9️⃣ Escape / Unescape:-
escapeXml(String str)
unescapeXml(String str)
escapeHtml(String str)
unescapeHtml(String str)

🔥 🔟 Compare Methods:-
equals(String str1, String str2)
equalsIgnoreCase(String str1, String str2)
contains(String str, String search)

🔥 1️⃣1️⃣ Length / Substring:-
length(String str)
substring(String str, int start)
substring(String str, int start, int end)

🔥 1️⃣2️⃣ Prefix / Suffix:-
startsWith(String str, String prefix)
endsWith(String str, String suffix)

🔥 1️⃣3️⃣ Misc Utility:-
reverse(String str)
repeat(String str, int times)
abbreviate(String str, int maxWidth)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔥 1️⃣ Basic Check:-
String str1 = "";
String str2 = "   ";
String str3 = "Hello";

System.out.println(StringUtil.isEmpty(str1));
System.out.println(StringUtil.isBlank(str2));
System.out.println(StringUtil.isNotEmpty(str3));

✅ Output:-
true
true
true
--------------------------
✅ safeTrim(String str):-
👉 null-safe trim (spaces hataata hai)
System.out.println(StringUtil.safeTrim("  Hello  "));
System.out.println(StringUtil.safeTrim(null));
✅ Output:-
Hello
""

✅ safeEquals(Object o1, Object o2):-
👉 null-safe comparison
System.out.println(StringUtil.safeEquals("abc", "abc"));
System.out.println(StringUtil.safeEquals(null, "abc"));
✅ Output:-
true
false

✅ safeToString(Object obj):-
👉 object → string (null safe)
System.out.println(StringUtil.safeToString(123));
System.out.println(StringUtil.safeToString(null));
✅ Output:-
123
""
----------------------------------------------------------
✅ stringToList(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.stringToList("A,B,C"));
👉 String → List

✅ Output:-
[A, B, C]

✅ stringToList(String str, String delimiter)
System.out.println(StringUtil.stringToList("A|B|C", "|"));

✅ Output:-
[A, B, C]

✅ listToString(List list):-
List<String> list = Arrays.asList("A", "B", "C");
System.out.println(StringUtil.listToString(list));
👉 List → String
✅ Output:-
A,B,C

✅ listToString(List list, String delimiter):-
List<String> list = Arrays.asList("A", "B", "C");
System.out.println(StringUtil.listToString(list, "-"));
✅ Output:-
A-B-C

✅ csvToList(String str):-
List<String> list = Arrays.asList("A", "B", "C");
System.out.println(StringUtil.csvToList("X,Y,Z"));
✅ Output:-
[X, Y, Z]

✅ listToCsv(List list):-
List<String> list = Arrays.asList("A", "B", "C");
System.out.println(StringUtil.listToCsv(list));
✅ Output:-
A,B,C
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
✅ join(Collection col, String delimiter):-
List<String> list = Arrays.asList("A", "B", "C");
System.out.println(StringUtil.join(list, ":"));
👉 items ko jodta hai
✅ Output:-
A:B:C

✅ split(String str, String delimiter):-
List<String> list = Arrays.asList("A", "B", "C");
System.out.println(StringUtil.split("A:B:C", ":"));
👉 string todta hai
✅ Output:-
[A, B, C]
-----------------------------------------------
✅ coalesce(Object... values):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.coalesce(null, null, "First", "Second"));
👉 first non-null value
✅ Output:-
First

✅ defaultIfNull(String str, String defaultVal)
System.out.println(StringUtil.defaultIfNull(null, "Default"));
👉 null ho toh default
✅ Output:-
Default

✅ Example 1:-
String str = null;
String result = defaultIfNull(str, "Hello");
System.out.println(result);
👉 Output:-
Hello
✔️ Kyunki str null tha → default value mil gayi

✅ Example 2:
String str = "Hi";
String result = defaultIfNull(str, "Hello");
System.out.println(result);
👉 Output:-
Hi
✔️ Kyunki str already value rakhta hai
----------------------------------------------------------
✅ capitalize(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.capitalize("hello"));
👉 first letter capital
✅ Output:-
Hello

✅ uncapitalize(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.uncapitalize("Hello"));
👉 first letter small
✅ Output:-
hello

✅ toUpperCase(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.toUpperCase("java"));
✅ Output:-
JAVA

✅ toLowerCase(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.toLowerCase("JAVA"));
✅ Output:-
java
-------------------------------------------------------------
✅ trim(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.trim("  Hi  "));

✅ Output:-
Hi

✅ trimToNull(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.trimToNull("   "));
👉 empty → null
✅ Output:-
null

✅ trimToEmpty(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.trimToEmpty(null));
👉 null → ""
✅ Output:-
""
-------------------------------------------------------------
✅ replace(String str, String search, String replace):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.replace("Hello World", "World", "Java"));
✅ Output:-
Hello Java

✅ remove(String str, String remove):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.remove("Hello World", "World"));
✅ Output:-
Hello 

✅ removeWhitespace(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.removeWhitespace("H e l l o"));
✅ Output:-
Hello
---------------------------------------------------------------------
✅ escapeXml(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.escapeXml("<tag>"));
✅ Output:-
&lt;tag&gt;

✅ unescapeXml(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.unescapeXml("&lt;tag&gt;"));
✅ Output:-
<tag>

✅ escapeHtml(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.escapeHtml("<h1>Hi</h1>"));
✅ Output:-
&lt;h1&gt;Hi&lt;/h1&gt;

✅ unescapeHtml(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.unescapeHtml("&lt;h1&gt;Hi&lt;/h1&gt;"));
✅ Output:-
<h1>Hi</h1>
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
✅ equals(String str1, String str2):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.equals("abc", "abc"));
✅ Output:-
true

✅ equalsIgnoreCase(String str1, String str2):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.equalsIgnoreCase("ABC", "abc"));
✅ Output:-
true

✅ contains(String str, String search):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.contains("Hello World", "World"));
✅ Output:-
true
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
✅ length(String str):-
System.out.println(StringUtil.length("Hello"));
✅ Output:-
5
----------------------------------------------------------------
